OPS 3.2.0 Release Notes
GIT tag: 3_2_0-4

Release date: November 7, 2022
==============================

3.2.0-4 Build
-------------
	#8307: SECURITY Validate author IDs against submissions/publications

Bug Fixes (-3 build)
--------------------
	#5588: Author list: author name is empty if not included in submission's metadata
	#5753: Submission checklist "edit" link leads to 404
	#5407: Use v-cloak to hide unstyled content flash before Vue kicks in
