	#5749: [OPS] Unable to delete Series/Section
	#5741: PostgreSQL "operator does not exist"
	#5735: Resolve SQL errors with picky PostgreSQL servers
	#5734: Component URL camelize/uncamelize functions do not use codesafe uc/lc functions
	#5725: Notification query getByUserId often run with no indexes used
	#5732: Cannot delete sections
	#5731: Autoloader does not use codesafe upper/lower functions
	#5718: Supporting Agencies field does not appear in submission process

